=== Test 1: SummingMergeTree Basic Tuple ===
Basic Tuple - with FINAL:
1	(250,110,2)
2	(450,165,2)
3	(650,185,2)
Basic Tuple - after OPTIMIZE:
1	(250,110,2)
2	(450,165,2)
3	(650,185,2)
Basic Tuple - access by position:
1	250	110	2
2	450	165	2
3	650	185	2
=== Test 2: SummingMergeTree Empty Tuple ===
Empty Tuple - with FINAL:
1	()	250
2	()	450
Empty Tuple - after OPTIMIZE:
1	()	250
2	()	450
=== Test 3: SummingMergeTree Nested Tuple ===
Nested Tuple - with FINAL:
1	(300,120,(500,18,(4,20)))
2	(400,140,(600,27,(6,30)))
Nested Tuple - after OPTIMIZE:
1	(300,120,(500,18,(4,20)))
2	(400,140,(600,27,(6,30)))
